The paper deals with secure communication networks and wiretapping, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of network coding also suggests a possible categorization under networked systems (cs.NI). The graph-theoretic approach used in the paper is also a common tool in computer science, which could place it under data structures (cs.DS) or social and information networks (cs.SI).
